title: AFC Hierarchy Report
itunes:title: AFC Hierarchy Report
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Dan Hanzus, Colleen Wolfe, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Derek Carr's record breaking contract and the Chiefs decision to part ways with GM John Dorsey. The heroes then welcome ATN voice over artist Alex Fragola on the podcast to field a few twitter questions. Conor Orr also joins Around the NFL for another edition of Orr you Kidding Me?!
